name: BAD BOY BLUE
description: Hidden deep within the harsh marshland swamp of FLUF World, lives Bad Boy BLUE. Born an orphan to parents who fought and perished during The Great Purge, BLUE holds a prophetic  secret. Unbeknownst to most FLUFs, BLUE is a direct descendant of the warrior clan of BLU. Legend has it that the BLU were the bravest of FLUFs, and have sworn a life binding oath to protect all fluffle tribes for millennia. It is said that only the bluest of BLU born in the swamp would attain pure blue warrior blood. The only FLUF born in the swamp after The Wreck, possessing Moody Blue Fur, deep Blue Eyes, and the fierce Expression of Anger, BLUE finds himself fulfilling an age old prophecy. As a young FLUF, he was visited by the spirit of COBALT the ancient one, who handed BLUE the most sacred items of his clan. Today, BLUE dons the Gold Studs of courage and the Gold Chain of leadership, and is last existing heir to an ancestral heritage of brave legendary FLUF warriors.

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: James Fluf Haskell
description: Just a simple, straightforward guy as life is too short to complicate and debate. What happened to the days of putting your hand right up, letting someone count and majority wins? I like to tackle my problems, hard and fast. People could argue that I come off too strong but Ive built a career off being a heavy hitter. Dont take everything too seriously, have a laugh and we will get along just fine. I want someone to look beyond the tough surface and strawberry blonde fur, yes my fur is strawberry blonde, I am not ginger and see me for who I really am. When Im not out on the field, Im in the kitchen cooking up my favourite chicken wings. I love to cook, come to think of it, there isnt a lot of things I dislike apart from perhaps short people. Im also a bunny of many ideas. Some creative, some controversial but have a tendency to slack on the execution and on the search for a special Fluf to help me do so. Did I mention I'm also a below average part time DJ
